{"tid":2046873,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Now新聞台: 祿泉樓四名確診者 居不同樓層但非同一座向","createTime":"2020-06-01T16:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T18:07:12.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"226b10741774696e817001bda291c82dfdbcb6ea","tid":2046873,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:47:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392987\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392987&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns80n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=b7770755\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392987&h=f9f97ef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392987</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】本港多三人確診新型冠狀病毒，均屬本地感染，與日前確診的瀝源邨女患者有關，其中一人為救護員，是首次有救護員因工作確診；另外消息指，瀝源邨祿泉樓再多四人確診。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，瀝源邨祿泉樓再多四人確診，全部都是經留低深喉唾液樣本化驗後確診。晚上有穿着整套保護衣的救護員到瀝源邨祿泉樓，用擔架床先後將病兩人送院，亦有人自行登上救護車。現場<span style=\"color: red;\">消息指，四名新確診患者，分別住在七、八及十樓，但不是同一座向。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058e9c8b39a4973fee2f057f860dce2d75cfb69e","tid":2046873,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:49:05.000Z","msg":"大爆發"},{"pid":"4e247ce4ff913d46046a6fb3750512418c37774e","tid":2046873,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:49:30.000Z","msg":"lift 傳播定又係屎渠"},{"pid":"a4e5a9d5a8ae1feaaf91109d8ee5daaf4923cf3f","tid":2046873,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"一個乞嗤打落街，樓下RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94df6e296bc9208e62ff91276e113c9ff59ee279","tid":2046873,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score